sys_documentation.hint: To filter assets by their name-fragment or any fragment in their text or number type fields. It’s case-insensitive.
sys_documentation.label: Seach Fragment
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Entity type and id of the entity the assets were linked to, separated by a slash character (accepted values: person, personGroup, branch, location, incident, changeActivity, knowledge, change, problem, omActivity, omSeries). For example: person/4878f620-e404-4f2d-9d53-622a1693d467
sys_documentation.label: Linked to
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Whether to include template information in the response. It can be one of the following: none (default if omitted), relevant (works only if linkedTo is present), all.
sys_documentation.label: Include Template Information
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Supports a limited set of simple odata filters. Filtering assets based on the objectid field with greater-than operator (Ex $filter=name gt ‘My Object’). Filtering assets based on date fields with greater-than, or less-than operator. Dates are interpreted as UTC dates (Ex $filter=modificationDate gt ‘2017’ and modificationDate lt ‘2017-05-26’). Supported formats: yyyy (2017); yyyy-MM (2017-12); yyyy-MM-dd (2017-12-25); yyyy-MM-dd’T’HH:mm (2017-12-25T18:30); yyyy-MM-dd’T’HH:mm:ss (2017-12-25T18:30:12); yyyy-MM-dd’T’HH:mm:ss.SSS (2017-12-25T18:30:12.798). Filtering based on a linked entity. Ex $filter=linkedTo eq 'incident/2eebf650-c5d7-4bf3-ad05-1f4cbced3b06’. Filtering based on a text field. Use the ‘contains’ operator. Ex $filter=specification contains 'desk’. Filtering based on a checkbox field on false and true values. Ex $filter=termsandconditions eq 'false’. Filtering based on a number field. Ex $filter=cost eq 15, $filter=cost ge 40. - - Filtering based on a dropdown field. Ex $filter=dropdown-field eq '2eebf650-c5d7-4bf3-ad05-1f4cbced3b06’.
sys_documentation.label: Filter
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: To filter assets by a specific template’s name (case sensitive).
sys_documentation.label: Template Name
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: To filter assets by their status. Possible values: OPERATIONAL, IMPACTED.
sys_documentation.label: Asset Status
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: When it’s given it returns more meta information, including all person and location related assignments. See ‘/assignments’ endpoint documentation for more details about the response format.
sys_documentation.label: Show Assignments
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: To filter assets by their name-fragment use this parameter. It’s case-insensitive.
sys_documentation.label: Name Fragment
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: To filter assets by a specific template. Since each asset type uses only one template, this filtering is the same as filtering between asset types.
sys_documentation.label: Specific Template ID
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Whether to show archived assets. Leave out for all, or specify true/false for only archived, or only active assets, respectively.
sys_documentation.label: Archived
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Influences the returned set of fields. It’s possible to give a comma separated list of field id-s of assets. The following fields are relevant for all assets: name, specification, @@summary, modificationDate, creationDate. If value is ‘default_grid_fields’ it returns default grid fields with more meta information.
sys_documentation.label: Fields
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9

sys_documentation.hint: Entity id of the entity the assets were linked to. Can be present only with linkedTo when only one instance exists and it doesn’t have entityId. (This parameter will be removed in one of the subsequent versions of the API. Use linkedTo instead.)
sys_documentation.label: Linked to Id (Deprecated)
sys_documentation.name: var__m_sys_hub_action_input_7e5fc9acdb305850f7b4f7461d9619f9
